# VibeStream Discovery & Parity Upgrade

We have completed the overhaul of VibeStream's discovery systems and achieved high-fidelity layout parity with YouTube Shorts.

## Phase 19: Discovery & Personalization
Implemented a robust tagging and categorization engine to fuel organic growth.
- **Intelligent Tagging**: A canonical library of the [Top 50 Tags](file:///C:/GOLive/lib/tags.ts) powers real-time autocomplete suggestions during upload.
- **Shorts Detection**: Vertical videos under 60s are automatically detected and flagged, ensuring correct grid placement.
- **Creator Config**: New "Primary Category" meta field in settings streamlines high-velocity recommendations.
- **Bento Profiles**: The channel "About" page now features a premium stats grid for subscribers and viral metrics.

## Phase 20: YouTube Shorts Parity
The `/shorts` player now matches the high-fidelity UI of industry leaders.
- **Action Bar**: Redesigned with "tonal" circular buttons and labels directly beneath for a sleek, modern feel.
- **Subscribe Integration**: Added a high-contrast white Subscribe button next to the creator handle.
- **Cinematic Ambient**: Optimized the background blur and dimming to fill non-vertical space with a high-fidelity glow.
- **Audio Pivot**: Added a rotating disc icon at the bottom right to highlight the audio track source.

